{"tid":1831321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［真相愈辨愈明］咩係人血饅頭？","createTime":"2020-01-20T10:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T11:11:26.000Z","uid":21678,"like":148,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"7eaa3c63d3c9d2aa049f6025308fc83b8c5561a0","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"紅媒鼓吹<br />\n任何黃色背景嘅人賺嘅任何錢，都係血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n佢哋用盡一切媒體，上至文滙大公支那01 TVB<br />\n下至<strong>連登三毛偷偷留下嘅comment</strong><br />\n總之要令你聽過幾百次<br />\n漸漸地覺得<br />\n<br />\n龍門係血饅頭<br />\n渣哥又係血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n黃圈又係血饅頭<br />\n光時又係血饅頭<br />\n重光號又係血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n黃子華又係血饅頭<br />\n阮民安又係血饅頭<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n總之任何支持革命嘅人，但係只要一有金錢瓜葛<br />\n唔駛審<br />\n呢條友就係「食人血饅頭」<br />\n<br />\n目的顯然易見<br />\n就係唔想你班香港人響革命運動中<br />\n得到金錢上嘅好處<br />\n因為佢地自知<br />\n好多藍絲之所以藍，只係因為一個錢字<br />\n如果黃圈行之有效<br />\n呢班人就會變節"},{"pid":"9d529ff1877c3bef8710f3569474b04454386b84","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:09:45.000Z","msg":"名不正則言不順<br />\n咁乜嘢先叫血饅頭？<br />\n如果冇釐清個概念<br />\n就永遠畀紅媒主導風向<br />\n<br />\n學術少少咁講<br />\n人血饅頭即係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主動借助其他手足嘅犠性而獲取利益</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n裡面幾個關鍵字：<br />\n<br />\n1. 主動<br />\n例如，兩個手足畀狗追<br />\n一個自己仆低畀狗咬<br />\n另一個趁機逃走<br />\n咁可唔可以話走得甩嘅人食另一個手足血饅頭？<br />\n當然唔可以<br />\n因為手足跌低，唔係另一位故意做成<br />\n就唔應該怪走得甩嘅人係食血饅頭"},{"pid":"6fc7a3b9846744b31a49b0b56d3f768c3a89ce46","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"2. 犠性<br />\n即係有一啲手足有金錢、身體、聲譽、法律等等各個方面嘅「損失」<br />\n如果有啲商業活動<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係冇人有任何損失<br />\n咁何血饅頭之有？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n又例如，有手足印咗「光復香港」嘅揮春<br />\n賣$1,000 蚊一張<br />\n<br />\n佢係咪發國難財？係<br />\n但有冇人因為咁而蒙受損失？冇<br />\n<br />\n呢一千蚊<br />\n畀嘅覺得值，收嘅夠膽收<br />\n純粹商業活動，你情我願<br />\n既然冇一個第三者響呢單交易當中被剝削<br />\n咁人血饅頭論亦唔應該成立<br />\n<br />\n觀乎榮光歲月<br />\n出嘅第一日<br />\n已經有一大堆打手話蘋果借呢本嘢嚟搵錢云云<br />\n但係嘅然冇人因為咁而受傷害<br />\n而又有咁多人想要本嘢紀念<br />\n咁印多幾本，有咩問題呢？"},{"pid":"38fe858f2d00de0eba93512fbf3e8ac10606e899","tid":1831321,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b168c7fbd2012f41a40b1817622b93edeb4f93","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:11:50.000Z","msg":"3. 利益<br />\n紅媒除咗金錢<br />\n仲連區會選票、議員知名度、甚至連光環<br />\n都會計算做佢地眼中「利益」嘅一部份<br />\n<br />\n連埋頭兩點<br />\n如果手足唔係主動傷害其他人<br />\n又或者冇人受到損失<br />\n咁畀自己人賺選票、賺光環<br />\n根本就係同時扶助緊運動本身<br />\n而唔係單純嘅個人利益<br />\n所以不存在咩血饅頭"},{"pid":"486cc0e84115a7de5a6e2e56659fbdbed30b0cfe","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:13:08.000Z","msg":"相反<br />\n而家整個革命變成長期消耗戢<br />\n手足最需要嘅<br />\n就係補給<br />\n<br />\n而做番手足生意，扶助黃圈<br />\n先至可以支撐運動一直咁維持落去<br />\n而且時間愈長<br />\n黃圈可以愈壯愈大<br />\n嬴面先至會變大<br />\n<br />\n手足嘅錢<br />\n唔止唔係血饅頭<br />\n仲係大家抗爭嘅重要資源<br />\n應該有咁多<br />\n食咁多"},{"pid":"3e0a64b7021a4694efa91924f4a6e5e976ebc07b","tid":1831321,"uid":65074,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:13:51.000Z","msg":"我唔介意有偽黃扮黃賺錢<br />\n起碼都識扮<br />\n好過班仲奶緊中共袋底果班"},{"pid":"945a10ab29de32a9cca522b5516d797d3e5c3887","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"如果可以嘅話<br />\n最好黃色商品<br />\n長做長有<br />\n甚至出現以質素互相兢爭嘅程度<br />\n咁先可以去蕪存青<br />\n亦可以修正唔合理嘅訂價<br />\n<br />\n黃圈唔止唔係施捨<br />\n仲要經良性兢爭做到質素並重"},{"pid":"94d6daa734338086edf604fff50220515830d623","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"而且愈有錢賺嘅產業<br />\n先可以吸引到愈頂尖嘅人參加<br />\n手足唔單止唔係做義工<br />\n仲可以發大財<br />\n黃圈先可以一日比一日壯大"},{"pid":"f74cae4548cb16ddacb841d241626f1c79fe57d3","tid":1831321,"uid":293896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62e6bbbd855e52582f051066539c931982d54a2","tid":1831321,"uid":173326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"關黃子華事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540a0e070e483134a36082774674eb0c47f5935b","tid":1831321,"uid":253952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94d6daa734338086edf604fff50220515830d623","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"而且愈有錢賺嘅產業<br />\n先可以吸引到愈頂尖嘅人參加<br />\n手足唔單止唔係做義工<br />\n仲可以發大財<br />\n黃圈先可以一日比一日壯大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"長遠要咁"},{"pid":"bc9cdf4c164c29a7615fb7aa06657325548019c8","tid":1831321,"uid":158662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"呢個真 有用 推"},{"pid":"dc8b2f87ff0bc8e138dedfaec8c838710fe14fed","tid":1831321,"uid":158662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"推多次"},{"pid":"6458a521655e645b49e3936a98f00492ed9d2601","tid":1831321,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"俾多d人見到"},{"pid":"4f49a0070be19fb88e70bed5eaf2f370d9aa23c1","tid":1831321,"uid":63029,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:23:54.000Z","msg":"血饅頭都係食包啫<br />\n<br />\n制度暴力賺緊血黃金、血鑽石"},{"pid":"cc8fed42daa593f8809cd6ba2606437cce44ecc2","tid":1831321,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:24:10.000Z","msg":"榮光聯盟 - 係小弟牽頭的，開個post俾大家屌，你問我答<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803947</a><br />\n<br />\n【警世】永續黃色經濟圈方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1828360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1828360</a><br />\n<br />\n[黃色經濟圈] 鼓勵創業 先係真正可持續嘅經濟圈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1829173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1829173</a>"},{"pid":"ea8b958c4f9a91f88ce66a62ed446a289b80e06b","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9e5f4ca6022d72d972099076fd6af89da0249e","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4f49a0070be19fb88e70bed5eaf2f370d9aa23c1","tid":1831321,"uid":63029,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:23:54.000Z","msg":"血饅頭都係食包啫<br />\n<br />\n制度暴力賺緊血黃金、血鑽石"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"港共就係想斷你財路<br />\n先至無所不用其極咁抺黑黃圈姐"},{"pid":"7d3f590177b927faa3ec4fd9044017057343d066","tid":1831321,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"你問吓有幾多人睇過篇《藥》先啦"},{"pid":"cf84166f72ea03996bf5e9fc2e20a881d21bf097","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"之前成堆人話和你宵血饅頭<br />\n設計收錢又血饅頭<br />\n變相推到門欖極高<br />\n只準手足做義工<br />\n<br />\n明顯對家就係想靠呢個講法<br />\n唔想手足響當中搵到錢<br />\n因為一搵到錢<br />\n其實手足甚至可以全職咁做<br />\n對政權嘅影響就會愈嚟愈大"},{"pid":"47c2852a70d6e3673a58c27f0ed89d7bb4e5cf38","tid":1831321,"uid":47968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.lcms.edu.hk/it-school/homepage/s98117756/read/11read/2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcms.edu.hk%2Fit-school%2Fhomepage%2Fs98117756%2Fread%2F11read%2F2.htm&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9wRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=f5e38f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lcms.edu.hk/it-school/homepage/s98117756/read/11read/2.htm</a>"},{"pid":"da73cf260067cef0bb1b73f19dbb7a49e42bc430","tid":1831321,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b88f2cc5cc42f210dd4b5a187e98a73b80ea971","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7d3f590177b927faa3ec4fd9044017057343d066","tid":1831321,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"你問吓有幾多人睇過篇《藥》先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:37:44.000Z","msg":"我都冇特登quote 返魯迅篇嘢<br />\n因為畀人講吓講吓<br />\n血饅頭而家已經唔係果個意思"},{"pid":"e8e3ecdfd286b63ff03a77b156ca6811bcb61c9b","tid":1831321,"uid":217270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3651a498936c9ef0732466f5e666c519ef68e61","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"540a0e070e483134a36082774674eb0c47f5935b","tid":1831321,"uid":253952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94d6daa734338086edf604fff50220515830d623","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"而且愈有錢賺嘅產業<br />\n先可以吸引到愈頂尖嘅人參加<br />\n手足唔單止唔係做義工<br />\n仲可以發大財<br />\n黃圈先可以一日比一日壯大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"長遠要咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:42:25.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n例如最好有第二間頂響龍門旁邊<br />\n啲嘢好食過佢<br />\n迫使龍門進步<br />\n雙方鬥好食鬥服務鬥黃<br />\n啲嘢食先可能好過敏華翠華太興之流"},{"pid":"5171baba3835f323da2843aaefb7c7b2aee10219","tid":1831321,"uid":237038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:42:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eace0db445da30b760170b0ea5efe97d129d7376","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:47:53.000Z","msg":"如果可以嘅話<br />\n最好呢半年以來嘅文宣<br />\n可以逐步商品化<br />\n<br />\n（例如嗰啲figure<br />\n真係高質到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n賺呢啲錢唔單止唔係血饅頭<br />\n更加係設計上嘅軟實力<br />\n可以幫助外國呢一啲圈子嘅人<br />\n都留意到香港嘅動態"},{"pid":"cea605b75279f16d40f01ee12fc5a09d1c24a542","tid":1831321,"uid":215472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:52:26.000Z","msg":"揾到錢之餘而又無忘本，繼續支持番黃圈其實ok"},{"pid":"291bb35556199bff0d09ab7b6da1bb4f32da4d26","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3e0a64b7021a4694efa91924f4a6e5e976ebc07b","tid":1831321,"uid":65074,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:13:51.000Z","msg":"我唔介意有偽黃扮黃賺錢<br />\n起碼都識扮<br />\n好過班仲奶緊中共袋底果班"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:53:39.000Z","msg":"如果偽黃扮黃<br />\n又成功搵到大錢<br />\n呢個至係最好嘅結局<br />\n<br />\n咁就會有一大堆黃皮藍心嘅人<br />\n至少響口頭上<br />\n都會同政府割蓆<br />\n<br />\n有咩畀睇住敵人嘅支持者倒戈<br />\n更加大快人心？"},{"pid":"8d58f7b1a8ca4349d9c8cb1196a8b954919805a9","tid":1831321,"uid":239689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46f18a20c2a6c587bffaa3cab4e6ea29121a693c","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa1b359ccd2ca83a37700acca4c27765ab60c9e","tid":1831321,"uid":9230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b88f2cc5cc42f210dd4b5a187e98a73b80ea971","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7d3f590177b927faa3ec4fd9044017057343d066","tid":1831321,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"你問吓有幾多人睇過篇《藥》先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:37:44.000Z","msg":"我都冇特登quote 返魯迅篇嘢<br />\n因為畀人講吓講吓<br />\n血饅頭而家已經唔係果個意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"所以仲有咩好辯？跟本一堆小學雞鸚鵡學舌"},{"pid":"820cfc3ee08228c0cd4608a116edb14f88dc928d","tid":1831321,"uid":21678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:03:42.000Z","